FBIS3-3818 "drchi057_a_94004" FBIS-CHI-94-057 Document Type:Daily Report 24 Mar 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS General Foreign Ministry Holds Weekly News Briefing Brazilian Foreign Minister To Visit OW2403081594 Beijing XINHUA in English 0750 GMT 24 Mar 94 OW2403081594 Beijing XINHUA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Beijing, March 24 (XINHUA) -- Celso Lafer, foreign minister of the Federative Republic of Brazil, will pay an official visit to China from April 3 to 6 at the invitation of Chinese Vice-Premier and Foreign Minister Qian Qichen . A Chinese Foreign Ministry spokesman made the announcement at a weekly press conference here today.
